# AssemblyScript diff-match-patch codec (bun run build:wasm). The .wasm artifact
# is committed (tiny, ~7 KB) so tests and Vercel use it without a build step; the
# .wat is a debug disassembly and is not.
src/core/assembly/build/*.wat
